ble towers packed with challenging combat scenarios, platforming bits and opportunities for creative environmental kills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>I will see you on the other side, Knight</i>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155650/extras/0727f3864ba94824ed0adce12ccf5875.poster.avif?t=1773858861\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155650/extras/0727f3864ba94824ed0adce12ccf5875.webm?t=1773858861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1155650/extras/0727f3864ba94824ed0adce12ccf5875.mp4?t=1773858861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
